current = [0.001, 0.005, 0.01, 0.02, 0.05, 0.1, 0.2, 0.5, 1.0, 2.0, 5, 10, 14];

[Is, n] = DiodeFit(voltage, current);
disp(Is);
```

This will display the value `4.6244e-06` for `Is`, which is the saturation current of the diode.

